io.github.eb4j.mdict.data

クラス DictionaryData<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.eb4j.mdict.data.DictionaryData<T>
  • 型パラメータ:
    T - The type of data stored

    public final class DictionaryData<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    A class that encapsulates the storage and retrieval of string-keyed data. Usage:
    1. Retrieve data with lookUp(String)
